data.description: Welcome to your dream home, where luxury meets comfort in a gated neighborhood! Beautifully maintained 2story, 3 bedroom home with 2 full baths, 1 half bath, game room and formal dining room. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living space and kitchen, creating an inviting atmosphere for both daily living and entertaining guests. The primary suite is a true retreat, complete with a full bath, sitting area, and generous closet space. The additional bedrooms share a well-appointed full bath, ensuring comfort for all residents and guests. NEW HVAC System & ROOF in 2018. Custom built storage racks in the garage. Never lose electricity with a 22kw Whole home GENERAC GENERATOR. Take advantage of the spectacular view of the neighborhood lake. Enjoy the serene private setting of your new backyard with a covered concrete porch. Full list of improvements available upon request. Call today for a private showing!
